    <ex:description>Levofloxacin should be discontinued if the patient experiences symptoms of neuropathy including pain, burning, tingling, numbness and/or weakness or other alterations of sensation including light touch, pain, temperature position sense and vibratory sensation in order to prevent the development of an irreversible condition.</ex:description>
